    Get bios

    get_cisbios.Rd

    Get a wide range of athlete-specific data.

    Usage

    get_cisbios(ibu_id)

    Arguments

    ibu_id

    Character. IBU athlete ID. Find it, e.g. by calling search_athletes() first.

    Value

    A list.

    Details

    Note: The list includes a wide range of information, nested in further lists which is time-consuming to expand into one 'tidy' data.frame. To get more specific information in tidy format, use the functions get_stats(), get_recent(), and get_ranks().
